**`creatio_test_security`** ŌĆö Runs automated security checks: OWASP Top 10 coverage, authentication bypass attempts, authorization boundary testing, input validation, and header analysis. Complements the InfoSec audit tools with active testing.

**`creatio_test_business_process`** ŌĆö Executes a business process in test mode and validates outputs, timing, and error handling. Accepts a `processName` parameter. Reports step-by-step execution results.

**`creatio_test_custom_scenario`** ŌĆö Executes a user-defined test scenario with scripted steps (API calls, assertions, wait conditions). Accepts a `steps` parameter with an array of test actions.

