**`creatio_test_regression_full`** ŌĆö Comprehensive regression test: schema integrity, data counts, API responses, process execution, and configuration drift. Compares against the last captured baseline.

**`creatio_test_report_export`** ŌĆö Exports test results in structured formats. Accepts a `format` parameter: `"pdf"`, `"json"`, or `"csv"`. Includes summary metrics, detailed findings, and trend charts.

